Class NameType

  • com.hp.jipp.encoding.NameType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AttributeType<T>

    public class NameType
implements AttributeType<T>

    An attribute type for name types, which can be encoded with either Tag.nameWithoutLanguage or Tag.nameWithLanguage.

    See RFC8011 Section 5.1.3.

    See Also:
    RFC8011 Section 5.1.3
